commit.message: Change get_shutdown_reason to recognize OS-based shutdowns
Add instance type to status report

Add discovery function,

also refactor id/short code validaton
Add extra utterances to all intents
Add test for invalid short code
Add error handling for short code and no instances
Add tests for start and stop functions

Correct indentation error

Rename id because it's a built in variable.

Alter id selection in handler to fix Lex input

Lex includes both slots in event, but the unused one will be set to None, so just check for value.

Add support for short code in place of id

Also, moved response generation to the handler so it's easy to pass session attributes around.
Alter output dict to match Lex format
Add test for bad instance id
